"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757793","Northern Ireland Office","false","2017-09-12","<p>Since the start of the 2016-17 year, my Department has only undertaken one procurement which has taken more than three months. This procurement took more than one year to complete.</p><p><strong> </strong></p>","Norwich North","Chloe Smith",,"2017-09-12T15:43:51.287Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757793/answer","Biography information for Chloe Smith","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757793/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757793/answer",,,,,"21","Northern Ireland","Northern Ireland","2017-09-05","Northern Ireland Office: Procurement","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland, how many procurements undertaken by his Department have taken more than (a) three months, (b) six months, (c) one year and (d) two years.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","8763"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757794","Prime Minister","false","2017-09-13","<p>I was accompanied on my visit by representatives from the Scotch Whisky Association. Further details regarding the visit can be found on the gov.uk website.</p>","Maidenhead","Mrs Theresa May",,"2017-09-13T12:52:01.263Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757794/answer","Biography information for Mrs Theresa May","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757794/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/757794/answer",,,,,"23","Prime Minister","Prime Minister","2017-09-05","Japan: Exports","1","House of Commons","To ask the Prime Minister, what steps she took to promote the export of Scotch whisky and other Scottish food and drink during her recent visit to Japan.","false","Biography information for Stephen Kerr","Stirling","Stephen Kerr","8904"
